<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">会上，市经信委主任顾向民指出本次化工企业联合执法检查要做到</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">明确责任，强化领导</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">密切配合，依法推进</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">总结经验，提升效果</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。一方面，检查组要按照全市</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“263”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">专项行动的总体部署和</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">工作方案要求，进一步细化工作任务、时序进度，合理安排好检查企业，提高工作效率，强化工作推进；另一方面，各部门既要各负其责，又要相互支持、密切配合，各司其职，确保联合执法检查取得实效。同时在联合执法检查工作推进过程中，做好总结工作，推广好的经验做法，改进不足之处，努力为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">工作夯实基础，全面落实</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减化</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">目标任务。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">副市长金健宏强调：一要明确化工企业整治的意义，联合执法检查的必要性；二要明确这次检查的范围和要求；三要抓好几个统一：将工作与维护社会稳定（协同信访等相关部门）、员工合法利益、生产安全结合起来；四要进一步发挥化工联席会议制度作用；五要加强组织领导，各部门要紧密配合。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
